OL,3,CMum spent final year in 'pain and
OL,4,Csqualor' after son pulled her out of
OL,5,Ccare home
OL,7,FOver the next year, Graham Walsh, of
OL,8,FBury New Road, sought no social care
OL,9,Ffor his mother and she was not seen by
OL,10,Fany medical professionals.
OL,12,FOn one occasion in December 2018,
OL,13,FWalsh called the emergency services
OL,14,Freporting that his mother had a very
OL,15,Fpainful leg. He mentioned that she had
OL,16,Fdementia, and he was unsure whether or
OL,17,Fnot she had hurt her leg in a fall.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
