OL,7,FHe later received a call from the out
OL,8,Fof hours doctor, but he informed them
OL,9,Fthat his mother was feeling better and
OL,10,Fwould not need assistance.
OL,12,FIt wasn't until 15 March 2019 that
OL,13,Fparamedics discovered the poor
OL,14,Fconditions in which Lillian lived,
OL,15,Fwhen Graham Walsh called emergency
OL,16,Fservices to report that his mother had
OL,17,Fbroken her leg.
OL,19,FWhen they arrived at his home, they
OL,20,Ffound his mother on a dirty mattress
OL,21,Fin "a state of undress".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
