OL,5,Ccare home
OL,7,FLilian was quickly taken to North
OL,8,FManchester General Hospital, where
OL,9,Fmedical staff noted a number of dirty
OL,10,Fbandages, multiple bruises and marks
OL,11,Fall over her body, wrist and face.
OL,12,FBasic hygiene issues were also noted.
OL,14,FDespite the best efforts of hospital
OL,15,Fstaff, Lilian died in hospital two
OL,16,Fdays later, on the evening of March
OL,17,F17th 2019.
