OL,7,FGraham Walsh was later charged with
OL,8,Ftwo counts of ill-treating or
OL,9,Fneglecting a person who lacks
OL,10,Fcapacity, to which he initially
OL,11,Fpleaded not guilty. But on the first
OL,12,Fday of his trial, Walsh changed his
OL,13,Fplea and admitted to both charges, and
OL,14,Fwill be sentenced on 27 March 2025.
