OL,7,FAlan Pope, Senior Crown Prosecutor for
OL,8,FCPS North West, said: "Lillian Walsh
OL,9,Fwas robbed of her dignity and suffered
OL,10,Fterribly during the last months and
OL,11,Fdays of her life, when her son, who
OL,12,Fshould have loved and cared for her
OL,13,Finstead left her to live in squalor.
