OL,3,CMum spent final year in 'pain and
OL,4,Csqualor' after son pulled her out of
OL,5,Ccare home
OL,7,F"Not only had he neglected her basic
OL,8,Fhygiene needs, but he had also failed
OL,9,Fto seek medical attention for her
OL,10,Fbedsores, and it was days before he
OL,11,Freported her injured leg. Everyone
OL,12,Finvolved in the case has been deeply
OL,13,Fconcerned by the complete lack of
OL,14,Fbasic care and compassion."
